snippet.title: Indian Gaming Future = @IndusGame  | Indus Battle Royale Gameplay Trailer Reaction!
snippet.description:

Trailer ka link - https://youtu.be/D5P7L5uU3-E

Aur aur aur, guys you can win some custom limited edition Indus x Techno t-shirts. Aapko sirf unke channel pe jaakar subscribe karna hain, aur unke Gameplay Trailer pe comment daalna hain - IndusXTechno. Main 100 community members ko T-shirt bhejne wala hoon. Tere Bin Episode 11 Teaser - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

SHAZAM! FURY OF THE GODS 
From New Line Cinema comes ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods,‚Äù which continues the story of teenage Billy Batson who, upon reciting the magic word ‚ÄúSHAZAM!,‚Äù is transformed into his adult Super Hero alter ego, Shazam. ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods‚Äù stars returning cast members Zachary Levi (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok‚Äù) as Shazam; Asher Angel (‚ÄúAndi Mack‚Äù) as Billy Batson; Jack Dylan Grazer (‚ÄúIt Chapter Two‚Äù) as Freddy Freeman; Adam Brody (‚ÄúPromising Young Woman‚Äù) as Super Hero Freddy; Ross Butler (‚ÄúRaya and the Last Dragon‚Äù) as Super Hero Eugene; Meagan Good (‚ÄúDay Shift‚Äù) as Super Hero Darla; D.J. Cotrona (‚ÄúG.I. Joe: Retaliation‚Äù) as Super Hero Pedro; Grace Caroline Currey (‚ÄúAnnabelle: Creation‚Äù) as Mary Bromfield / Super Hero Mary; Faithe Herman (‚ÄúThis Is Us‚Äù) as Darla Dudley; Ian Chen (‚ÄúA Dog‚Äôs Journey‚Äù) as Eugene Choi; Jovan Armand (‚ÄúSecond Chances‚Äù) as Pedro Pena; Marta Milans (‚ÄúWhite Lines‚Äù) as Rosa Vasquez; Cooper Andrews (‚ÄúThe Walking Dead‚Äù) as Victor Vasquez; with Djimon Hounsou (‚ÄúA Quiet Place Part II‚Äù) as Wizard.  Joining the cast are Rachel Zegler (‚ÄúWest Side Story‚Äù), with Lucy Liu (‚ÄúKung Fu Panda‚Äù franchise) and Helen Mirren (‚ÄúF9: The Fast Saga‚Äù).  The film is directed by David F. Sandberg (‚ÄúShazam!,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnnabelle: Creation‚Äù) and produced by Peter Safran (‚ÄúAquaman,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù). It is written by Henry Gayden (‚ÄúShazam!,‚Äù ‚ÄúThere‚Äôs Someone Inside Your House‚Äù) and Chris Morgan (‚ÄúFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Fate of the Furious‚Äù), based on characters from DC; Shazam! was created by Bill Parker and C.C. Beck. Executive producers are Walter Hamada, Adam Schlagman, Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Victoria Palmeri, Marcus Viscidi and Geoff Johns.  Joining director Sandberg behind-the-camera are director of photography Gyula Pados (the ‚ÄúJumanji‚Äù franchise), production designer Paul Kirby (‚ÄúThe Old Guard,‚Äù ‚ÄúJason Bourne‚Äù) and editor Michel Aller (‚ÄúShazam!,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù). The music supervisor is Season Kent (‚ÄúDC League of Super-Pets,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Addams Family 2‚Äù) and the music is by Christophe Beck (‚ÄúFree Guy,‚Äù ‚ÄúFrozen II‚Äù). Visual effects supervisors are Bruce Jones (‚ÄúAquaman,‚Äù ‚ÄúIt‚Äù) and Raymond Chen (‚ÄúAlita: 
Battle Angel,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù). The costume designer is Louise Mingenbach (‚ÄúJumanji: The Next Level,‚Äù ‚ÄúGodzilla: King of the Monsters‚Äù).  New Line Cinema presents A Peter Safran Production of A David F. Sandberg Film, ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods,‚Äù which is set to open in cinemas in India beginning March 17, 2023.

snippet.title: SRK‚Äôs Pathan Brings Box Office Tsunami - Supreme Leader Reacts | Akash Banerjee
snippet.description:
Supreme Leader is Pissed. India was just the start - Now Pathan is creating global Box Office records. snippet.title: Republic Day 2023 |  Highlights Of The Republic Day Parade 2023 | 26th January 2023 Parade | News18
snippet.description:
Republic Day 2023 |  Highlights Of The Republic Day Parade 2023 | 26th January 2023 Parade | News18 

The 74th Republic Day Parade was about the spectacular display of made-in-India weapons, increased role of 'Nari Shakti' in the Armed Forces and signs of the country leaving behind its colonial past. For the first time in the history of India‚Äôs Republic Day, the British-era 25-pounder guns, which had been used for decades for the 21-gun salute, were replaced with the indigenous 105mm Indian Field Guns. The vintage artillery, which was once used in the World War II, fell silent and the desi guns boomed for the ceremonial gun salute. Lt Commander Disha Amrith, 29, was the first Navy woman officer to lead a naval contingent of 144 sailors, showcasing the increasing role of 'Nari Shakti' in the military. Armed with assault rifles, women soldiers in colourful uniforms, usually deployed along the desert border with Pakistan, were for the first time joined the BSF camel contingent. Women officers were also part of the contingents of Corps of Signals, Army Air Defence and Army Daredevils

snippet.title: SHAZAM! FURY OF THE GODS - Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
It's Time To Grow Up. Shazam! Fury of the Gods ‚Äì in theaters March 17. #ShazamMovie

SHAZAM! FURY OF THE GODS 
From New Line Cinema comes ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods,‚Äù which continues the story of teenage Billy Batson who, upon reciting the magic word ‚ÄúSHAZAM!,‚Äù is transformed into his adult Super Hero alter ego, Shazam. ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods‚Äù stars returning cast members Zachary Levi (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok‚Äù) as Shazam; Asher Angel (‚ÄúAndi Mack‚Äù) as Billy Batson; Jack Dylan Grazer (‚ÄúIt Chapter Two‚Äù) as Freddy Freeman; Adam Brody (‚ÄúPromising Young Woman‚Äù) as Super Hero Freddy; Ross Butler (‚ÄúRaya and the Last Dragon‚Äù) as Super Hero Eugene; Meagan Good (‚ÄúDay Shift‚Äù) as Super Hero Darla; D.J. Cotrona (‚ÄúG.I. Joe: Retaliation‚Äù) as Super Hero Pedro; Grace Caroline Currey (‚ÄúAnnabelle: Creation‚Äù) as Mary Bromfield / Super Hero Mary; Faithe Herman (‚ÄúThis Is Us‚Äù) as Darla Dudley; Ian Chen (‚ÄúA Dog‚Äôs Journey‚Äù) as Eugene Choi; Jovan Armand (‚ÄúSecond Chances‚Äù) as Pedro Pena; Marta Milans (‚ÄúWhite Lines‚Äù) as Rosa Vasquez; Cooper Andrews (‚ÄúThe Walking Dead‚Äù) as Victor Vasquez; with Djimon Hounsou (‚ÄúA Quiet Place Part II‚Äù) as Wizard.  Joining the cast are Rachel Zegler (‚ÄúWest Side Story‚Äù), with Lucy Liu (‚ÄúKung Fu Panda‚Äù franchise) and Helen Mirren (‚ÄúF9: The Fast Saga‚Äù).  The film is directed by David F. Sandberg (‚ÄúShazam!,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnnabelle: Creation‚Äù) and produced by Peter Safran (‚ÄúAquaman,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù). It is written by Henry Gayden (‚ÄúShazam!,‚Äù ‚ÄúThere‚Äôs Someone Inside Your House‚Äù) and Chris Morgan (‚ÄúFast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Fate of the Furious‚Äù), based on characters from DC; Shazam! was created by Bill Parker and C.C. Beck. Executive producers are Walter Hamada, Adam Schlagman, Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Victoria Palmeri, Marcus Viscidi and Geoff Johns.  Joining director Sandberg behind-the-camera are director of photography Gyula Pados (the ‚ÄúJumanji‚Äù franchise), production designer Paul Kirby (‚ÄúThe Old Guard,‚Äù ‚ÄúJason Bourne‚Äù) and editor Michel Aller (‚ÄúShazam!,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù). The music supervisor is Season Kent (‚ÄúDC League of Super-Pets,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Addams Family 2‚Äù) and the music is by Christophe Beck (‚ÄúFree Guy,‚Äù ‚ÄúFrozen II‚Äù). Visual effects supervisors are Bruce Jones (‚ÄúAquaman,‚Äù ‚ÄúIt‚Äù) and Raymond Chen (‚ÄúAlita: 
Battle Angel,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù). The costume designer is Louise Mingenbach (‚ÄúJumanji: The Next Level,‚Äù ‚ÄúGodzilla: King of the Monsters‚Äù).  New Line Cinema presents A Peter Safran Production of A David F. Sandberg Film, ‚ÄúShazam! Fury of the Gods,‚Äù which is set to open in theaters internationally beginning 15 March 2023 and in North America on March 17, 2023.

#tamiltrekker #mongolia #coldest 

Hey backpackers, get ready for my exciting Mongolia series. Here's my vlog for the first day, sharing my day-1 experience with -27 degrees Celsius. 

My new year's first international trip started in Mongolia, and you can't imagine the freezing weather that welcomed me! If you're looking for a pleasant season to visit Mongolia, I recommend visiting when it's less cold. 

Watch my latest travel vlog to learn about Mongolia's relationship with India, local travelling, and more.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3678 - 26 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3678: Taarak Ka Luck
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak finally gets ready in Iyer's yellow shirt. Meanwhile, everyone from Gokuldham pays him a visit to wish him luck on his big day. Popatlal, out of concern, catches a random guy from a temple who was wearing a yellow shirt. He wanted to take the yellow shirt off the guy and give it to Taarak. Anjali feels gratified about being surrounded by such caring Gokuldham people. Taarak's boss video calls him to check on his yellow shirt. After such a conundrum, will everything fall into place? Will Taarak be able to attend the meeting in the yellow shirt? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3678, 26 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

About Film Companion South:
Film Companion South is a division of Film Companion, founded by film critic and author Anupama Chopra. Apart from film reviews and articles, Film Companion South, with programs in Tamil, Malayalam, Telugu, and Kannada, specializes in conducting in-depth interviews with film personalities which include the likes of Kamal Hassan, Mani Ratnam, Academy Award-winner AR Rahman, Vetrimaaran, Dhanush, Yash, Sruthi Hariharan, Mahesh Babu, NTR Jr, Samantha, Aishwarya Rajesh, Ramya Krishnan, Prithviraj, Anjali Menon, Mysskin, Gautam Vasudev Menon, Rajamouli, Ram Charan, Yash, Prashanth Neel, Venkat Prabhu, Nelson, Sivakarthikeyan, Rakshit Shetty and many more. The channel has also hosted shows which open up the lesser-known facets of filmmaking with conversations with PC Sreeram, Ravi Varman, Rajiv Menon, Thota Tharani, and Academy Award-winner Resul Pookutty. In other words, Film Companion South is for those who love their cinema and are unapologetic about it.

snippet.title: Meri Baari | @IqlipseNova | New Hindi Song 2023
snippet.description:
‚ÄúNo matter where you come from, if you can dream about it, you can get it ‚Äú

Says Iqlipse Nova as he presents a song that is an announcement and a celebration. Fresh off his viral single Mera Safar, singer-songwriter Iqlipse Nova is back with is latest drop, Meri Baari. With this one, he continues to tell his story about his dreams and goals in his own unique way.

#meribaari #iqlipsenova #merasafar #hindisong  #motivationalsong #newmusic #viral #trending #reels
Song credits : 
Sung, written and composed by Iqlipse Nova ( https://www.instagram.com/iqlipse_nova/?hl=en)
Music Producer : WhySoAryan
Backing Vocals : Harry Arora
Mixed by : Harry Arora

Shoot location- IM BUILDCON- Applaud38, Goregaon East¬†https://instagram.com/imbuildcon?igshid=YWJhMjlhZTc=¬†https://applaud38.com/?fbclid=PAAab-Fw4P-AlyyxwpBxQ-Op1CN58i8bydGg_Hpdx5xUpT-XlQ52LyLPlCmWk

Lyrics:
Do chaar hi yaar hai mere,
Apno se door yahan pe,
Ghar wale sath nahi hai,
Na hai mera pyar yahan pe,

Yun toh hai hota nahi,
Kuch bhi sahi, jo bhi main karu..  
Fir bhi hai mann ye mera, mane nahi,
Kyu hi main daru!

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari.

Sapne dekhe jo kabhi the,
Poore kar lu main wo saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari‚Ä¶

Maine maar dekha, maine thoda pyar dekha
Maine haar dekha, toota wo guitar dekha 
Beeti thi raatein meri Dilli ki sadko pe,
Pocket mein sikka le, Sapne hazar dekha‚Ä¶

Na piya daru, kabhi liya nahi Vape par, 
Deta main heart, apne hateron k hate par..
Label bhi rota mere gaano k han rate par 
Khali main hoon baitha phir bhi jaata nahi date par..

Gaana bhi toh Gaana hai na, 
Legacy banana hai na,
Time thoda kam hai, Netflix pe bhi aana hai na, 
Jo bhi hai bola mujhe karke dikhana hai na,
Aaane wale saalon, Maa ko mumbai bhi toh lana hai na.

Jana hai na, han mujhe kal world tirp pe, 
Plane mein raat, han meri subhe hogi ship pe,
Saans k jaise loon main shares har dip pe, 
Hoga zamana meri ungli k tip pe‚Ä¶

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari.

Sapne dekhe jo kabhi the,
Poore kar loon main wo saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aagayi hai meri baari‚Ä¶

Meri Baari, Meri Baari
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Meri Baari, Meri Baari
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Ye Khumari, hai khumari,
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Meri Baari, Meri Baari
Aagayi hai Meri Baari

Kaise main bhoolun abhi,
Maa ki wo baatein sabhi,
Chota sa ghar wo mera,
Apne mere, Galiyan meri

Toota dil bhi tha kabhi,
Yaad aaye college abhi,
Dilli ki sardiyon si,
Raatein nahi, hoti kahin!

‚Äî‚Äî

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aa gayi hai meri baari.

Khush rehne ki hai Bimari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Kal ki Chinta na mujhe hai,
Aa gayi hai meri baari.

Meri Baari,
Jalti hai ye duniya saari,
Hai Khumari,
Aa gayi hai meri baari.

Meri Baari‚Ä¶
